question: Where can I find fast food restaurant located en route to Go Ape Treetop Adventure Course, Strongsville, OH from Country Inn & Suites, Elyria, OH, within a radius of 160 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-82.118609 41.401075)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.818381 41.322133)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-82.118609 41.401075)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-82.118609 41.401075)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Portage Path Broaster and Mini Mart

[4].display_name: Go Ape Treetop Adventure Course, Strongsville, OH
